But you know what? There's no limitation to you in your relationship with the Father.

00:46:42.459 --> 00:46:48.319
I'm tired of bringing man into my equation. I don't need man; I need Jesus.

00:46:48.320 --> 00:46:58.879
And in him, he has everything I need. He has everything I need. I don't need a touch from a man; I need a touch from Jesus.

00:46:58.880 --> 00:47:04.919
He may use a man to bring it sometimes, but ultimately, I need to sit at his feet.

00:47:04.920 --> 00:47:08.888
But whenever you sit at his feet, you can have everything that's in his hand.

00:47:08.889 --> 00:47:16.119
You can have it. Whatever he has, you can have because you're in covenant with him.

00:47:16.120 --> 00:47:20.479
So, Father, we thank you, Lord, that you're a covenant-keeping God.

00:47:20.480 --> 00:47:39.398
And the same covenant that you made with Abraham, the same covenant that you had with Moses, that you would bless Abraham's generation over a thousand generations—I believe that you are still a covenant-keeping God, and, Father, we're your people.

00:47:39.399 --> 00:47:48.679
We are your children, your church. And we are blood-bought, the redeemed, the church. We're the blood-bought church, the redeemed.

00:47:48.680 --> 00:47:55.651
And I believe, Father, that right now you are pouring out that Spirit on us like we should be walking in.

00:47:55.652 --> 00:48:04.220
I told D, I said, "I'm tired of feeling like we're pushing through this."I went to the other side of it.

00:48:04.221 --> 00:48:12.483
You know what I'm talking about? That Holy Ghost and fire, believing for what I'm talking about—all those scriptures.

00:48:12.484 --> 00:48:18.279
I said, "Lord, whatever it takes in me that's holding back anything, change me.

00:48:18.280 --> 00:48:24.719
I am on your potter's wheel. Fix this."Because Brandon—I'm telling y'all, Brandon's got issues.

00:48:24.720 --> 00:48:29.568
We all got something we're working through. We're all a work in progress.

00:48:29.569 --> 00:48:34.347
But I don't want my cup to be really shallow; I want my cup to be deep.

00:48:34.348 --> 00:48:41.079
And I want my cup to run over. Surely goodness and mercy will follow me all the days of my life.

00:48:41.080 --> 00:48:50.290
And there's an overflow of his mercy. There's an overflow of his goodness. So now I'll pray in the spirit for a little bit.

00:48:50.291 --> 00:48:55.239
I told you all that, I try to stir you up with what the Holy Ghost has given me today for you.

00:48:55.240 --> 00:51:53.199
But let's pray in the spirit. You want to? So, Father... I'm seeing a building again.

00:51:53.200 --> 00:52:11.457
I see a building, and at the top, at the very top, it's all on fire.

00:52:11.458 --> 00:52:16.410
All four—I see one, two, three, there's for sure three sides.

00:52:16.411 --> 00:52:22.143
I can't see the other side. And, you know, it's a glass front all up.

00:52:22.144 --> 00:52:43.479
It's really, really beautiful. It's a really square building.

00:52:43.480 --> 00:52:51.101
But on the very top—it's not all the way up to the top, it's right towards a quarter of the way—and there's fire all around it.

00:52:51.102 --> 00:52:56.536
And the fire is burning outward. It's burning outward of this building.

00:52:56.537 --> 00:57:47.999
It's an attack. Come on. He sings a song over you today. He sings a song over you today.

00:57:48.000 --> 00:57:55.435
There's a rain. I see rain. I see the rain again. I see the rain.

00:57:55.436 --> 00:58:03.008
I see a rain coming. I see a rain, a refreshing on those dry bones.

00:58:03.009 --> 00:59:39.506
On those dry bones, I see a refreshing of the rain. I forgot I was doing a live. I get caught up in it. I could see over there, I was looking.

00:59:39.508 --> 00:59:51.159
Many of you—the Lord said—many of you, there have been great attempts to keep you off track from where he's called you to be.

00:59:51.160 --> 00:59:58.993
Family, friends, relatives of all kinds, but they've put a snare.

00:59:58.994 --> 01:00:11.766
And it's like when you keep slipping in it, and you keep slipping in it, and you can't seem to get any traction to walk through it.

01:00:11.767 --> 01:00:21.999
And it's time you put those people that are on the sidelines—the peanut gallery—out of your mind and do what God's called you to do.

01:00:22.000 --> 01:00:27.319
You need to hear me. There's a peanut gallery always telling you, "Well, you're not good enough.

01:00:27.320 --> 01:00:36.239
You've not walked good enough. You've not done this. You've not done that. Well, you're not educated. You don't have what it takes.

01:00:36.240 --> 01:00:40.119
Well, you know, you've been this way and you'll probably always be this way."You've got to tell the peanut gallery to get out of your way.

01:00:40.120 --> 01:00:48.599
You've got to do what God has called you to do. You're running out of time.

01:00:48.600 --> 01:00:55.374
God has put his hand on you from a child, and you have to shake off the peanut gallery.

01:00:55.375 --> 01:01:00.235
I understand there are always going to be people that tell you you don't have what it takes.

01:01:00.236 --> 01:01:05.432
There are always going to be people that say, "Well, you've been broke, you'll always be broke."You'll never be broke.

01:01:05.433 --> 01:01:13.839
But God can turn it on a dime. God can turn your circumstance, and you don't need what you think you needed.

01:01:13.840 --> 01:01:22.615
God can open the doors that no man can open. You don't need man; you need a Father. You need Jesus.

01:01:22.616 --> 01:01:29.559
And he'll open the doors for ministry for you whenever he sees that you're ready for it.

01:01:29.560 --> 01:01:36.239
I thought for all the time of my life that it was going to be who I rubbed shoulders with.

01:01:36.240 --> 01:01:50.319
"Well, if I put myself around this person, if I put myself around that person, maybe they'll see me and know me, and they'll give me an opportunity to speak or do whatever."But the Lord never allowed that one time.

01:01:50.320 --> 01:01:56.279
He said to me, "Brandon, what I'm about to do with you, no man will get the glory for.

01:01:56.280 --> 01:02:05.319
No man will get the glory for."And over this course of time, he said, "Just go on YouTube and I'll do the rest."He breathed on it.

01:02:05.320 --> 01:02:10.359
It had nothing to do with Brandon or Diana. Nothing to do with us.

01:02:10.360 --> 01:02:21.483
It had everything to do with obedience and a God that said, "I say it's time."And we limit God in our own minds by thinking that's how he has to operate.

01:02:21.484 --> 01:02:28.599
Well, it'll be by our pastor, it'll be by an evangelist, it'll be by sister so-and-so.

01:02:28.600 --> 01:02:34.559
"If I just serve them, if I do this, if I do that, if I could just be their armor bearer..."No.

01:02:34.560 --> 01:02:43.219
Whatever he tells you to do, do it. You know what he told me recently? Even was it three days ago, wasn't it, Braden?

01:02:43.220 --> 01:02:56.079
He said this: "You'll become more reclusive, yet I've called you to be separate. I don't want anybody influencing you.

01:02:56.080 --> 01:03:14.799
I want you to speak exactly what I tell you to say when I tell you to say it, and put your pink shorts on."He said, "So the things that you have in your mind of how it's going to work out, it ain't me. Stop allowing your flesh to dictate how you do things.

01:03:14.800 --> 01:03:27.319
Just flow with the voice of God, and he'll put you in front of the people he needs to put you in front of."How many times I've told people, "No, I don't want to do that interview.""Well, that'll get you really promoted.

01:03:27.320 --> 01:03:35.919
That'll get you exposure."I don't need your exposure; I need Jesus. Do you understand?

01:03:35.920 --> 01:03:43.919
Whatever he tells you to do, he'll blow on it, and he creates something out of nothing.

01:03:43.920 --> 01:03:51.673
He can create something out of nothing if you can just give him your undivided attention and your yielded heart.

01:03:51.674 --> 01:04:01.224
And all that you do, in word and in deed, do all to the glory of God. And he'll go. And that's what he did.

01:04:01.225 --> 01:04:04.139
I tried to be around the biggest pastors, the biggest ministers.

01:04:04.140 --> 01:04:10.839
"Oh Lord, that's going to get me there."And every single one of them said, "Nope."And finally, I gave up.

01:04:10.840 --> 01:04:21.399
And it was at my place of death and surrender at the altar that God said, "Now you're ready."I said, "I don't want to do this anymore. I can't do this.

01:04:21.400 --> 01:04:35.406
I can't fix Megan."Whenever I let go of Megan in my heart, my little girl, is when God started doing a miracle in her life, and she's getting better and better, and you can see her.

01:04:35.407 --> 01:04:45.128
She sits in service. We couldn't go to church before. It's when I let go of what I thought I could help him fix—I had my hand in it.

01:04:45.129 --> 01:04:57.159
God doesn't need your help; he just needs your surrender. God doesn't need your help; he needs your surrender.

01:04:57.160 --> 01:05:04.387
And that's where I met him, at my surrender. I said, "Lord, I can't do this anymore.

01:05:04.388 --> 01:05:11.719
I cannot provide for my family anymore. I'm tired of living on minimum wage.

01:05:11.720 --> 01:05:20.519
I'm tired of living on food stamps."And at my point of surrender, God started giving me ideas for money.

01:05:20.520 --> 01:05:26.439
God started teaching me, but it wasn't overnight. It was a process.

01:05:26.440 --> 01:05:33.006
As you do this, as you walk, as you obey—as they went, they were healed.

01:05:33.007 --> 01:05:34.759
As they went, they were healed. And I latch onto that: as they went, they were healed.

01:05:34.760 --> 01:05:49.543
As they went, they were made prosperous as they do what he tells them to do.

01:05:49.544 --> 01:05:56.514
As they went, what did he tell you to do? "Go dip in the river seven times."That's crazy.

01:05:56.515 --> 01:06:23.159
Do it. So all that. He'll take your little and make it a lot. He'll expand your baskets full twelve times over if you just believe him.

01:06:23.160 --> 01:06:30.961
He'll stretch your cap, your little of what you have, and make it a lot. "Well, I don't have much left.

01:06:30.962 --> 01:06:43.331
I don't have that."It only took the widow that was talking to Elijah a little flour and a little oil to stretch forth a lot.

01:06:43.332 --> 01:06:50.559
God has to take your little and will turn it into a lot if you just obey what he asked you to do.

01:06:50.560 --> 01:06:59.115
He takes the widow's mite and says, "She gave all that she had, but she gave more than them because she gave from her heart."You understand?

01:06:59.116 --> 01:07:07.879
God will breathe upon your little like he did with the widow, what he did with the fishes and the loaves.

01:07:07.880 --> 01:07:13.235
He's into showing up and showing off, and doing shock and awe in your life.

01:07:13.236 --> 01:07:20.546
He wants to show how big he is. And I remember even as a boy, we sow and my parents would sow.

01:07:20.547 --> 01:07:24.502
We all sow. We all give, and we have nothing, and God comes through.

01:07:24.503 --> 01:07:28.293
There's never been a time that I've never had food in my stomach.

01:07:28.294 --> 01:07:33.959
I've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

01:07:33.960 --> 01:07:38.428
That's what David said. I believe that God is able to provide.

01:07:38.429 --> 01:07:52.590
Whenever I told you I saw the people with what's coming, praying around pots of food, and there were empty pots, and they just set the table and they did it by faith, and they laid their hands—they all gathered around the table and they started praying.

01:07:52.591 --> 01:08:04.572
They said, "Father, we don't have nothing but whatever we have, there was a little there, multiply it."And all of a sudden it was bountiful.

01:08:04.573 --> 01:08:12.119
It was so much. And there was steam coming off the beans, and there was steam coming off the cornbread, and there was steam coming off the hot potatoes.

01:08:12.120 --> 01:08:18.053
God will show up in the least. I'm telling you folks, you need to believe him for the supernatural.

01:08:18.054 --> 01:08:24.454
That's where I've been. That's why I keep raising my kids. I know that God is able.

01:08:24.455 --> 01:08:29.279
Even whenever I hear her laughing in there right now—she's laughing, she ain't crying.

01:08:29.280 --> 01:08:40.879
I don't know if you can hear. I'd bring her in here and let her talk to y'all. Let Megan say, "Hi,"because she's come so far.

01:08:40.880 --> 01:08:44.144
And I believe there are so many of you who say, "Brandon, I have a child with special needs.

01:08:44.145 --> 01:08:51.399
Will God do it for mine?"If he did it for me—you don't realize how bad she was.

01:08:51.400 --> 01:10:13.399
You don't realize how bad Megan was and how far she has come. It seems so impossible.

01:10:13.400 --> 01:10:24.799
It seems so impossible, but he specializes in the impossible.

01:10:24.800 --> 01:10:34.271
"Their hearts are too hard toward me."I hear someone say, "Their hearts are just too hard toward me.

01:10:34.272 --> 01:10:43.999
My circumstances will never change."Well, I'm going to tell you, God specializes in the impossible.

01:10:44.000 --> 01:11:46.159
My father specializes in the impossible. Now, many of you think, "Well, he forgot about the building with the fires."No, I still see it.

01:11:46.160 --> 01:11:54.799
I see it right now. But you see, I'm not moved by that building with the fires.

01:11:54.800 --> 01:12:06.559
I'm not moved by it. The Lord wanted to minister to your heart.

01:12:06.560 --> 01:12:23.039
It's in Chicago. Just remember that. That's Chicago. Yeah, it's the building in Chicago.

01:12:23.040 --> 01:13:32.439
Is that okay? If you live in Chicago, this act is a distraction from something else.

01:13:32.440 --> 01:13:39.319
I'm allowed to say that something else is going to happen at the exact same time this is happening.

01:13:39.320 --> 01:13:48.131
I'm in the spirit. I can see it. This is to attract everyone there while something happens over here.

01:13:48.132 --> 01:14:06.159
It's sleight of hand. It's sleight of hand. Like you know what I'm talking about. Sleight of hand. This is over here.

01:14:06.160 --> 01:14:14.759
They're doing this over here to try to pull the law enforcement and all them over here while they do something major over here.

01:14:14.760 --> 01:14:18.240
And as everybody's fleeing here, they do something over here.

01:14:18.241 --> 01:14:23.719
And this is very serious over here. And this is the prime target.

01:14:23.720 --> 01:14:59.559
This is the prime target. No, it will happen all at the same time.

01:14:59.560 --> 01:15:07.039
You hear me? I see it all right now. I'm looking into it really well.

01:15:07.040 --> 01:15:34.159
I see it. You know what I'm talking about, Braden. I see it really clear.

01:15:34.160 --> 01:15:41.391
Is there a river that runs through there? What is that? Like there's like a river that is running through Chicago.

01:15:41.392 --> 01:15:52.679
It's like a stream. What is that water there? What is that? Am I looking at Chicago?

01:15:52.680 --> 01:16:08.479
I see water. No. Lord said, "Brandon, that's Boston. You're looking at two different places at one time.

01:16:08.480 --> 01:16:15.594
Two places at one time. Boston has water. I see water running through Boston.

01:16:15.595 --> 01:16:30.699
It's like a river, like a stream running through Boston. Chicago is the cities. It's the five. We're praying into those five cities, son.

01:16:30.700 --> 01:17:03.080
It's the five: Chicago, Boston, Philadelphia, New York, Washington."He said, "You're not praying into all of them right now.

01:17:03.081 --> 01:17:09.919
You're praying into two, one in particular, and that is Chicago."Okay?

01:17:09.920 --> 01:17:19.079
All at the same time. Do you get that? We're praying in. They're all on the same time.

01:17:19.080 --> 01:17:25.039
They're not all separate. They're separate events all on the same day.

01:17:25.040 --> 01:18:02.568
Okay. So I see: five. One, two, three, four, five. So that's what we're praying into.

01:18:02.569 --> 01:18:16.239
When we're praying into that, it's an onion that has layers.

01:18:16.240 --> 01:19:24.799
I see the Boston Fire Department. I see the men in the fire uniforms praying over them.

01:19:24.800 --> 01:20:57.611
Later, you see my phone, son. The Lord said, "Give me..."I can't say it out loud.

01:20:57.613 --> 01:21:36.119
He said, "This is concerning Austin."Oh, Father, I pray over the fire department, the first responders, the ones that are there first.

01:21:36.120 --> 01:21:58.279
Oh God, let everything be uncovered as they are the first responders.

01:21:58.280 --> 01:22:28.079
Let every booby trap be uncovered. I see one man. He is bald-headed like me.

01:22:28.080 --> 01:22:38.519
He has a mustache—a black mustache, but it's not thick; it's very thin.

01:22:38.520 --> 01:22:46.559
He has brown eyes and he's pretty round-headed. I see him run in there first.

01:22:46.560 --> 01:22:57.359
I see this man; he's very clear to me. He's the first one, and we pray over him.

01:22:57.360 --> 01:23:23.559
He has a family. I see his family, and we pray. Oh God, Father, I thank You that You protect this man.

01:23:23.560 --> 01:23:30.066
The others—the flash of the fire can drive the others. It's a backdraft.

01:23:30.067 --> 01:23:40.239
It's like this fire comes out of this thing, and he's engulfed, but these others are burnt really bad.

01:23:40.240 --> 01:23:58.719
I can see them really clearly. Whoever these men are, Lord, I pray for protection around and about our fire department.

01:23:58.720 --> 01:24:05.039
Father, have mercy on them. Father, I thank You that the angels of the Lord...

01:24:05.040 --> 01:24:33.879
I see a white dove intervening, causing a distraction. It's a tripwire.

01:24:33.880 --> 01:25:14.349
Fly up by the tripwire. Expose every plan, every plot of the wicked. Every tripwire, I see it. It's like in a hall.

01:25:14.350 --> 01:25:53.759
It's an apartment room that's rigged; it's an apartment that's rigged. I see it so clearly.

01:25:53.760 --> 01:25:57.999
We pray over every single one of them that You'll spare their lives, Father.

01:25:58.000 --> 01:26:25.333
Protect them. I thank You for Your angels. I thank You, Father. In every city, You expose them.

01:26:25.334 --> 01:29:33.119
That's what I got in the spirit right then: in every city, You'll expose them.

01:29:33.120 --> 01:29:56.279
We're in times like you've never seen before. Yep, for sure.

01:29:56.280 --> 01:30:07.617
And they will accelerate as labor pains upon a woman. I told you from September 23rd, watch the victory.

01:30:07.618 --> 01:30:12.799
A great acceleration has happened so far, just like He said it would.

01:30:12.800 --> 01:30:25.641
And it will continue to grow, and it will be compounding. It will be like a snowball rolling down the hill, gaining momentum.

01:30:25.642 --> 01:30:45.319
That momentum will grow, and it will be with your weather, it will be with your heavens, it will be with your earth's crust, it will be with your politics, and it will be with your church.

01:30:45.320 --> 01:30:55.839
Remember, this is an acceleration so much so that all of them will happen at the same time, at a point in time.

01:30:55.840 --> 01:31:06.079
It won't just be one thing. Politics, war, rumors of war—it will be all of them compounding, is what He's saying.

01:31:06.080 --> 01:31:15.700
You'll turn on your news and every day you'll see all of it like dominoes. You have never seen what you're about to see.

01:31:15.701 --> 01:31:26.796
I hear the Spirit of the Lord say to me, "You need to get your house in order.

01:31:26.797 --> 01:31:36.654
Get ready."Get ready, for a great humbling is coming. A great manifestation of the glory is coming.

01:31:36.655 --> 01:31:42.860
You need to get your house in order. Repent; turn from your wicked ways.

01:31:42.861 --> 01:31:50.884
You're running out of time each day. The clock is ticking, and in the hourglass, the sand is flowing.

01:31:50.885 --> 01:32:09.599
Remember, you're running out of time. You must get on the boat in time with your heart today.

01:32:09.600 --> 01:32:25.142
Change and repent before it's too late. You say, "Well, I haven't seen anything.

01:32:25.143 --> 01:32:35.439
I haven't seen this."Open your eyes. Look around you. And it's not all about America.

01:32:35.440 --> 01:32:41.559
It's a Western culture to always think that way—that it's about us, it's about America, America first.

01:32:41.560 --> 01:32:53.839
No, it's about the world. Watch what God does with the whole world.

01:32:53.840 --> 01:33:04.549
Isn't that amazing that you can pray like this in a hotel room and the Spirit of God fill a hotel room like this? It's so thick, I'm telling you. And I'm in a hotel room.

01:33:04.550 --> 01:33:20.326
I was leery of doing this in a hotel room, and I said, "Let's do it."I felt pressed of the Lord to do it, but it's like at the house—whoever's going to get this hotel room next, it'll fill them, I tell you that.

01:33:20.327 --> 01:33:26.639
It's saturating this chair. I feel that weight of that prophetic mantle.

01:33:26.640 --> 01:34:06.662
It comes down on me. Be the watcher. Glory to God! You see, we have to go.

01:34:06.663 --> 01:34:12.788
We'll be late for the church service tonight. It's getting late.

01:34:12.789 --> 01:34:20.839
We only have 30 minutes, and it takes a little bit to get there.

01:34:20.840 --> 01:34:31.903
Glory to God. I know, baby, we have to go. I prayed for almost an hour and a half, didn't I, son?

01:34:31.904 --> 01:34:43.033
Mama said, "Are you still alive?"I said, "Yeah, we're still alive."Well, regardless of whether I feel released yet, I have to go to this service.

01:34:43.034 --> 01:34:52.319
I want to be a part of this prayer service. It's important. The Lord said, "Assemble yourselves."We have 5,400 right now.

01:34:52.320 --> 01:35:05.559
He said, "You have to go assemble yourselves together and pray."Each one brings their part, each one brings their supply, and I believe that's what's so important about these prayer services.

01:35:05.560 --> 01:35:11.738
We all bring our supply. Thank you for watching today. We'll do it again tomorrow.

01:35:11.739 --> 01:35:20.558
I'll pray more. I have a good internet connection here, so I can pray with y'all.

01:35:20.559 --> 01:35:28.886
I'll eat and see what the Lord has for us. I was praying about going to Billy Burke in Tennessee.

01:35:28.887 --> 01:35:37.634
I was going to do a broadcast with Kim Clement's daughter, Donne, so I don't know if I'm going to do that still.

01:35:37.635 --> 01:35:44.599
I'm just flowing with what the Holy Spirit wants me to go and do, and we'll see.

01:35:44.600 --> 01:35:50.959
I'm excited to be here around all these prayer warriors, and I'm so thankful.

01:35:50.960 --> 01:36:01.466
I pray this blessed you, this little hour and a half. I'm sorry it couldn't be more, but I'll go now and start driving over there.

01:36:01.467 --> 01:36:09.420
Thank God, Mike told me he'd sow a seed tonight. So, thank God for Mike; he's my friend.

01:36:09.421 --> 01:36:16.209
God bless you all. Do they have any questions? Are they okay?

01:36:16.210 --> 01:36:27.836
Everybody's good. Happy birthday, Braden. Thank you. He's a good boy.

01:36:27.837 --> 01:36:33.519
He got blessed at Billy Burke. I'm telling you, the power of God knocked him down.

01:36:33.520 --> 01:36:43.582
He got a touch from Jesus. Every one of my family got a word from the Lord. At the Billy Burke meeting, it was beautiful.

01:36:43.583 --> 01:36:49.679
